{"word":"G2008 - ἐπιτιμάω - epitimáō - ep-ee-tee-mah'-o - Charge","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτιμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>epitimáō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-tee-mah'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அதட்டு, கடிந்து கொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to show honor to, to honor"},{"paragraph":"2. to raise the price of"},{"paragraph":"3. to adjudge, award"},{"paragraph":"4. to tax with fault, rate, chide, rebuke, reprove, censure severely"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5091 - τιμάω - timáō - tim-ah'-o/5091\">G5091</a>; to <i>tax upon</i>, that is, <i>censure</i> or <i>admonish</i>; by implication <i>forbid:</i> - (straitly) charge, rebuke."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2008 - ἐπιτιμάω - epitimáō - ep-ee-tee-mah'-o/2008\">G2008</a>, <a href=\"#/G2009 - ἐπιτιμία - epitimía - ep-ee-tee-mee'-ah/2009\">G2009</a>"}]}